wiki.summary: It's an unit song consisting of the members J-Hope, Jin, and Jungkook of BTS. In terminology, 'Jamais Vu' is french for "never seen". It is the phenomenon of experiencing a situation that one recognizes in some fashion, but nonetheless seems very unfamiliar or unknown. It is the opposite of 'Deja Vu'. It's most commonly experienced when a person momentarily does not recognize a word or, less commonly, a person or place, that they know. The song was released on April 12, 2019. It's the sixth track of the mini-album Map of the Soul: Persona. Read more on Last.fm.
